    var order = new Order { Items = { new OrderItem("SKU-1", 2) } };
    processor.CalculateTotal(order);

    processor.ApplyDiscount(order, "SAVE10");

    Assert.IsTrue(order.TotalAmount < 100m, "Discount should reduce total");
}
```

**Risk if unfixed:** Failure diagnosis becomes time-consuming — any of 7 methods could be the cause.

